Package ie.atu.sw

Class Outputter

java.lang.Object
ie.atu.sw.Outputter
public class Outputter extends Object
Outputter - Methods for outputting complete indexes to file or console. Extra options for output presented upon completion. See methods printSortedWords, printRevSortedWords, printUniqueWords, printMostFrequentWords.
Since:
JDK 19
